item.title: CVE-2023-0280|2024-08-02T05:02:44.093Z -- unknown -- ultimate%20carousel%20for%20elementor
item.description: The Ultimate Carousel For Elementor WordPress plugin through 2.1.7 does not validate and escape some of its block options before outputting them back in a page/post where the block is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
